text: ' is an Apollo asteroid and a near-Earth object discovered in September 2013 by the Catalina Sky Survey. The asteroid is roughly 300 meters in diameter. It was listed on the Sentry Risk Table in September 2013.http://neo.jpl.nasa.gov/risk/removed.html It was detected by radar soon after discovery.Broadband Photometry of the Potentially Hazardous Asteroid 2013 RH74 On 2013-Oct-17 the asteroid passed from Earth. ==See also== * List of Apollo asteroids ==References== == External links == * * * # Category:Minor planet object articles (unnumbered) # # # 20130908
